  25 May 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/libtorrent-0.6.2-fbsd.patch, libtorrent-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Added Gentoo/FreeBSD compatibility patch, now libtorrent compile and works
  there.

